title: Brody Jenner, 36, takes his young girlfriend Josie Canseco, 22, partying
text:
Brody Jenner seems to be spending a lot of time with his new model girlfriend Josie Canseco, who is the daughter of pinup Jessica Canseco and athlete Jose Canseco.

On Thursday evening the photogenic pair were seen together again as they joined friends for dinner in West Hollywood.

This comes just after the 36-year-old ex of Kaitlynn Carter filmed the 22-year-old blonde beauty working out in her grey bra at home.
